narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Orlando Health Inc. is a General Acute Care Hospital provider based in Orlando, FL. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $105.4M in Medicaid payments across 3.3M claims serving 0 beneficiaries.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: This provider received $105.4M in taxpayer-funded Medicaid payments — enough to fund healthcare for approximately 13,180 Medicaid beneficiaries for a full year at average per-enrollee costs.
